You’ll spot striking illustrations by Taiwan artist, Sean Wei, a versatile creative talent. The solo show【LOVE & ATTACK 】of Sean's works will be exhibited at the Pachamama Cafe. 【Music Party｜18.00- 24.00｜Sat 22 August 2015 】Free entry

The music party is opening to public, we are more then happy to have you and your friends, the more the merrier!
